hcc_text: Macombs Road is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Macombs Road at West 176th Street, Nelson Avenue and Dr M L King Jr Boulevard, there were 2 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
